@startuml
title "UC-03: Track Order Status"

actor Customer
participant "Mr. Daebak System" as System

== Initial Load ==
Customer -> System: 1. Request order list
activate System
System --> Customer: 2. Order list with current statuses
deactivate System

== Realtime Updates ==
Customer -> System: 3. Connect to realtime updates (WebSocket)
activate System
System --> Customer: 4. Connected

... time passes ...

System --> Customer: 5. Order status changed notification\n(order_id, old_status, new_status)
deactivate System

